{"tid":1848523,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 聯盟規例集中討論","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T03:40:41.000Z","uid":83648,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66d3fee1a0d736cb634a8e4174be962ee4443a4a","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"本身睇開足波<br />\n但年年都係某幾隊玩晒覺得好悶<br />\n所以就想知究竟有啲咩叫公平啲嘅規則<br />\n<br />\n無意中發覺NBA聯盟係設定公平競爭框架算比較成熟<br />\n但自己本身唔係藍球Fans所以好多都一知半解<br />\n所以開呢個post向各位藍波迷請教吓<br />\n亦都可以畀各位足波迷了解吓所謂公平啲嘅League係點"},{"pid":"ffb480d31fd98c1f625e2f67eba88f55ab88c042","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"首先想問吓球隊資薪問題<br />\n即係salary cap<br />\n<br />\n聯盟應該係每年計返收入再擬訂出每隊球隊該年可以有幾多錢簽人<br />\n<br />\n2019-2020 嘅球員薪金上限係$109 m美元<br />\n即係99m歐元<br />\n即84m 英鎊<br />\n<br />\n而每隊最少14名球員<br />\n最高15名球員<br />\n<br />\n即係呢班球員係呢一年就必須係109m 美元"},{"pid":"645edbac0c06d89916d9f4f4c756b90fb75d5836","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"如果超過109m美金係要罰豪華稅<br />\n<br />\n但想問係一超過109m就罰定點？<br />\n如果有個油王大把錢<br />\n唔怕罰稅<br />\n咁係咪就可以組幾個全明星巨頭隊？"},{"pid":"8d5befd1ce648057ffadc3555c44c4b05deaa2a5","tid":1848523,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"唔撚駛理 邊隊好波睇邊隊<br />\n同埋啲規則會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea2b306bd6ec2b33e39858a1e3f2aad38335d36","tid":1848523,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"645edbac0c06d89916d9f4f4c756b90fb75d5836","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"如果超過109m美金係要罰豪華稅<br />\n<br />\n但想問係一超過109m就罰定點？<br />\n如果有個油王大把錢<br />\n唔怕罰稅<br />\n咁係咪就可以組幾個全明星巨頭隊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"好似有hard cap"},{"pid":"3547ede71e0abf7f033c6688eeb688b3da8b64e0","tid":1848523,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0228afc69218df9229a79704c798a5ddd141a408","tid":1848523,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"I offer my sincere condolences to the family and friends of Kobe. 🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"e0a3d14e4f3be19b20022108c0ecf8d1cc88c998","tid":1848523,"uid":224771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645edbac0c06d89916d9f4f4c756b90fb75d5836","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"如果超過109m美金係要罰豪華稅<br />\n<br />\n但想問係一超過109m就罰定點？<br />\n如果有個油王大把錢<br />\n唔怕罰稅<br />\n咁係咪就可以組幾個全明星巨頭隊？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"過豪華稅就開始罰 越罰越甘<br />\n倍數上 同埋好似新班主入主要聯盟同意<br />\n應該發生唔到曼城咁既"},{"pid":"d5056afa4d589d54ed5fdc3c30b5fa535d4541e4","tid":1848523,"uid":298237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a3d14e4f3be19b20022108c0ecf8d1cc88c998","tid":1848523,"uid":224771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645edbac0c06d89916d9f4f4c756b90fb75d5836","tid":1848523,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"如果超過109m美金係要罰豪華稅<br />\n<br />\n但想問係一超過109m就罰定點？<br />\n如果有個油王大把錢<br />\n唔怕罰稅